704205f-a.text:
The intersection of Flatbush Ave. and Park Place at Seventh Ave. The trolley tracks run northward on Flatbush Ave. At the left is the Durfey house, on the corner of Seventh Ave. and Park Place; beyond it appear
Nos. 8-12 Seventh Ave. and the west side of Park Place.
About 1912.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

704206f-a.text:
319-325 Flatbush Ave., north side, at the intersection of Park Place and Seventh Ave. In the foreground is a car, the Seventh Ave.
Line and in the background the Flatbush Ave. Line.
November, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
